  "subject": "Added multiplatform jobs for policy-api image",
  "commit_message": "Added multiplatform jobs for policy-api image\n\nThis is a follow-up to patch https://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/ci-management/+/92707\nModified the policy-api project to use the multi-arch templates on\nmaster branch. This patch needs to be merged in sync with\nhttps://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/policy/api/+/93957\n\npolicy-api.yaml code rebased with master branch\n\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-217\nSigned-off-by: Srinivasan Selvam <srinivasan.s.n@huawei.com>\nChange-Id: Ifb486a09bf35c7d749bcd5571b3dfd3049d6bab5\n",
